explanations.reason: The paper focuses on identifying biomarkers for hepatocellular carcinoma (HCC) using network-based bioinformatics methods, such as gene expression profiling and protein-protein interaction (PPI) network analysis. There is no mention of any machine learning techniques, neural networks, or related methodologies in the title or abstract. The study primarily involves statistical and bioinformatics approaches rather than the listed machine learning or deep learning keywords.
